:: Ending 1 {"position":"2100,300","size":"100,100"}
The monster collapses, leaking dark fluid across the floor.

Your home is safe.

(if: $injured)[
But the scars on your face will never fade.
]

You survived.

THE END


:: Ending 2 {"position":"2100,500","size":"100,100"}
There is no pain.

Only darkness.

THE END


:: Ending 3 {"position":"2100,700","size":"100,100"}
You live.

But whatever now lives in your house…
knows you’ll never return.

THE END


:: Entrance {"position":"1100,500","size":"100,100"}
You stand still, listening.
The house feels wrong, heavier than usual, as if something else is here with you.

(if:  $ateFood is true)
[
Your stomach tightens. Something smells *off*.
]

What do you do?

[[Carefully follow the trace->INVESTIGATE]]
[[Ignore it like nothing happened->IGNORE]]


:: GO HOME {"position":"900,500","size":"100,100"}
After you open the entrance of your home you encounter a mess in your house.
Not the usual one you leave behind before leaving, this looks like a disaster a hurricane could have left.

On the floor you spot a trace of food.
Not one in particular, but a mixture of many things that were probably stolen from your kitchen.

[[Continue->Entrance]]



:: IGNORE {"position":"1300,400","size":"100,100"}
(set: $panicked to true)
(set: $injured to true)

You acted like nothing happened.
Just another mess you’ll clean “later”.

Then, it attacked you.

Something jumped from behind and latched onto your head.
You manage to pull it off, screaming.

A leech-like creature, almost the size of a dog, crawls on the floor.

[[Continue->STARE AT MONSTER]]


:: INVESTIGATE {"position":"1300,600","size":"100,100"}
(set: $heardMonster to true)

You slowly follow the trail.
A wet, shuffling sound echoes through the house.

Then you see it.

A leech-like creature, huge, with spider-like legs and a circular mouth full of grinding fangs.

It turns toward you.

It jumps.
You dodge just in time.

[[Continue->STARE AT MONSTER]]


:: STARE AT MONSTER {"position":"1500,500","size":"100,100"}
The creature freezes.
Its legs tremble.
It’s listening.

(if: $injured)[
Blood drips onto the floor.
The creature reacts to the sound.
]

What do you do?

[[Stay still->STILL]]
[[Grab something and attack->ATTACK]]
[[Run for the door->ESCAPE]]


:: STILL {"position":"1700,500","size":"100,100"}
You freeze.
Even your breathing feels too loud.

The creature turns away, distracted.

[[Strike now->ATTACK]]
[[Remain perfectly still->STILL2]]
[[Sneak toward the exit->ESCAPE]]


:: STILL2 {"position":"1900,500","size":"100,100"}
You don’t move.
Not even to breathe.

The creature suddenly turns back.

This time, it doesn’t hesitate.

[[Continue->Ending 2]]



